### Modul 1 — Unit Pendidikan (`education_levels`)
#### [NEW] EducationLevelController.php
- [index()](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Http/Controllers/DashboardController.php#26-62) — list semua unit + search
- `create()` / `store()` — form tambah + validasi
- `edit()` / `update()` — form edit + validasi
- `destroy()` — soft delete (atau hard delete karena data fondasi)

#### [NEW] views/education-levels/index.blade.php
