## Verification Plan

### Automated — Route List Check
```bash
cd /Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app
php artisan route:list --path=/ 2>&1
```
Pastikan semua resource routes terdaftar.

### Browser Test (per modul, via browser tool)
Untuk setiap modul:
1. Buka URL index (mis. `http://127.0.0.1:8000/education-levels`)
2. Klik "Tambah" → isi form → submit → verifikasi data muncul di tabel
3. Klik "Edit" → ubah data → submit → verifikasi perubahan tersimpan
4. Klik "Hapus" → verifikasi data hilang dari tabel

### Data Integrity Check
```bash
php artisan tinker --execute="echo App\Models\EducationLevel::count();" 2>&1
```
